Package: projectDependencyAnalyser
Type: Package
Title: R Project Workflow Analysis and Automation
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2025-01-16
Authors@R: person("Simon", "Dedman", email = "simondedman@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Comprehensive toolkit for analyzing R project workflows. Automatically
    catalogs file dependencies, determines script execution order, creates network
    visualizations, annotates scripts with dependency information, and converts
    workflows to the targets package format for automated reproducible pipelines.
